# anthropic.list — Anthropic / Claude
# Target group: Claude  (Select-only, default Taiwan)
# Source of truth for the build; policy/group is assigned at build time.
# Format: one rule per line, TYPE,value  (NO trailing policy).
# Add new Claude/Anthropic domains here — no config surgery needed elsewhere.
#
# See docs/adr/ADR-0001-claude-taiwan.md and docs/adr/ADR-0004-select-only-ai.md
DOMAIN-SUFFIX,claude.ai
DOMAIN-SUFFIX,anthropic.com
DOMAIN-SUFFIX,claude.com
DOMAIN-SUFFIX,claudeusercontent.com
DOMAIN-KEYWORD,anthropic
